类 AbstractImmutableSet<E>

  • java.lang.Object

    E -

    直接已知子类:
    ImmutableHashSet

    public abstract class AbstractImmutableSet<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Set<E>
    Skeleton class of immutable set. Just wraps the actual map class and all non-destructive method call is delegated to the wrapped object, and all destructive method call throws UnsupportedOperationException.
